Package org.zaproxy.zap.session

Class ScriptBasedSessionManagementMethodType

java.lang.Object
org.zaproxy.zap.session.SessionManagementMethodType
org.zaproxy.zap.session.ScriptBasedSessionManagementMethodType
public class ScriptBasedSessionManagementMethodType extends SessionManagementMethodType
The type corresponding to a SessionManagementMethod for web applications that use Session Management Scripts, which can hopefully model any custom behaviour required
Since:
2.9.0
